26â†’{"id":"br-2re","title":"Move CLAUDE.md to ~/claude/ as canonical location â€” hard link back to ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md","description":"CLAUDE.md currently exists as separate files in both ~/claude/CLAUDE.md (6.9k, full version) and ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md (1.1k, smaller version). The canonical location should be ~/claude/CLAUDE.md (git-tracked). A hard link back to ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md ensures the CLI reads it. Note: CLI may overwrite the file, so hard link (not symlink) is preferred per MEMORY.md patterns.","acceptance_criteria":"~/claude/CLAUDE.md is the canonical, git-tracked copy. Hard link at ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md points to same inode. Both files have identical content. Edits from either location are reflected in both.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-20T12:54:05.215628832Z","created_by":"skogix","updated_at":"2026-02-21T14:44:55.414421624Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["migration","preserve"]}
